<div id="ConsultingInfo">
<p>
The Beautiful Social Research Center is a digital media collaborative that is directed by the Communication and Digital Media Department at St. Joseph's University. 
Beautiful Social works with nonprofit organizations in the Philadelphia area to "increase their digital presence and to create a connection with their client base using social media platforms.
</p>
<p>
As a consultant, I have worked with various organizations. I consulted with John Heinz Wildlife Refuge and formulated a social media strategy for their Facebook page.
As a project manager, I have managed Communications with student-consultants and organizations such as Young and Involved Philadelphia and Project HOME.
</p>
<p>
You can check out an example of our work here.
</p>	
